                "title": "行相"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素伤害</span>，目标角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">蕴种印</span>；如果在附属前目标角色已附属有<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">蕴种印</span>，就改为对所有敌方角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">蕴种印</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/9ee7deb6582de98819a51f65d4d0a5e4_8875207332508225268.png",
